{"tid":1010448,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鄉議局為港求得車公86籤　解曰：家宅不吉求財不遂　","createTime":"2019-02-06T04:07:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-06T08:48:42.000Z","uid":160807,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a5711d29de0e9e78d8d1648dfe823589aef638ff","tid":1010448,"uid":160807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T04:07:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190206/photo/bkn-20190206082552136-0206_00822_001_01b.jpg?20190206120057\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190206%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190206082552136-0206_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20190206120057&h=45d6ec20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日(6日)是農曆大年初二車公誕，不少市民會到車公廟上香求籤轉風車，祈求新一年事事順境。新界鄉議局主席劉業強按習俗，早上率領沙田鄉事委員會代表及眾鄉紳，到沙田車公廟為香港求籤祈福。經過三叩首及上香參拜等儀式後，劉為香港豬年運程求籤，並求得第86號中籤。<br />\n<br />\n第86號籤籤文為：<strong>「石田為業喜非常，畫餅將來未見香；怎曉田耕耘不得，那知餅食不充腸。」</strong>解曰：<strong>「出入謹慎．家宅不吉．自身平安．求財不遂。」<br />\n</strong><br />\n劉稱該籤是吉籤，意思是香港基礎很好，但規劃及政府施政要市民支持，才會有更好的明天。對於籤文解曰「家宅不吉」，他則稱只要市民同心協力，排除萬難，必可修成正果。<br />\n<br />\n之後到沙田鄉事委員會首副主席李志麒為沙田求籤，他求得第82號下籤，籤文為：「心中日復自思量，時運未通怎主張；進退難為無定處，恐防患禍與災殃。」解曰：「出入謹慎．凡事小心。」<br />\n<br />\n今年求籤的位置改為在正殿進行，出席的立法會議員只有葉劉淑儀。因應去年求籤期間出現混亂，導致鄉議局所求的籤與沙田鄉事委員會所求的籤調亂，故今年安排了2個司儀，一人負責處理一項求籤，避免烏龍事件再現。<br />\n<br />\n另外，早上約7時45分，已有不少市民到車公廟上香祈福，不過期間發生小插曲，有善信不小心撞冧鐵欄，但保安很快便將鐵欄扶起。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190206/photo/bkn-20190206082552136-0206_00822_001_06b.jpg?20190206120057\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190206%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190206082552136-0206_00822_001_06b.jpg%3F20190206120057&h=74cedb57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n葉劉淑儀(左)派利是給曾舞麒麟撞飛她的謝師傅(右)。(梁家寶攝)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190206/photo/bkn-20190206082552136-0206_00822_001_02p.jpg?20190206104851\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190206%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190206082552136-0206_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20190206104851&h=8e7eee72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n出入謹慎．家宅不吉．自身平安．求財不遂。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190206/bkn-20190206082552136-0206_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190206%2Fbkn-20190206082552136-0206_00822_001.html&d=fwxP8pl6u%2F9ArYBpkrNVTFA4V8ywhhxRXFDRWvztIyc%3D&h=fa5d452d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190206/bkn-20190206082552136-0206_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"54c6de6826de05f21826d0651a4cca28ebc69dd7","tid":1010448,"uid":47954,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T04:14:29.000Z","msg":"今年發叔冇去求籤？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b8eaaefe4917de1b3ac38d09c3976dcbede1d7a","tid":1010448,"uid":160807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"54c6de6826de05f21826d0651a4cca28ebc69dd7","tid":1010448,"uid":47954,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T04:14:29.000Z","msg":"今年發叔冇去求籤？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T04:16:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0c055f14ac65d440409caee00c4b78213414f79","tid":1010448,"uid":41308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T08:41:09.000Z","msg":"都要同呢條友開年<br />\n<br />\n政府禍港政策都要支持？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不如叫政府唔好離地仲好"},{"pid":"afd0e0125ad497e0189f9eff71771d6df4b658fc","tid":1010448,"uid":10757,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T08:46:55.000Z","msg":"葉劉淑儀(左)派利是給曾舞麒麟撞飛她的謝師傅(右)。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=